{showImpuleFit || showNetflixClone || showSubmitForm || showTalkATive || showSite ? (
showImpuleFit(false) || setShowNetflixClone(false) || setShowSubmitForm(false) || setShowTalkATive(false) || setShowSite(false) } className="backdrop" >
) : null}
